Female/immature.description: Female/immature Blackburnian Warblers have a streaked back while female/immature Cerulean Warblers have a clean back. Also note triangular ear patch not seen on Cerulean Warblers.

Nonbreeding female/immature.description: Nonbreeding Blackpoll Warblers have a streaked back and orangish legs and lack the strong eyebrow of Cerulean Warblers.
